    Text: The gunwitch has doubts about this course of action.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: She is worried her gun is being used for evil
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The goblin tells her this is the only way to get that shipment of explosives
