  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: She stops herself and says its the only way to stop the trade. Sometimes
      you have to do some dirty work to do whats right.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The gunwitch calls her out for wanting to get the explosives for herself.
  - IndexCharacterRight: 0
    IndexCharacterLeft: 0
    IndexCharacterFocus: 0
    IndexExpression: 0
    IndexEmotion: 0
    Text: The gunwitch is conviced for now. She can at least control the goblin so
      she doens't do anything bad with the explosives
